  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<ul>
<li><strong>Studios &amp; Apartments:</strong> All have south-facing balcony or terrace, small kitchenette with 2 hot-plates, fridge and microwave oven, bath, hairdryer, cable TV, radio, telephone and coffee making facilities.</li>
<li><strong>Studio (A3) Sleeps 1-3:</strong> Living/dining room with 2 beds and one convertible bed.</li>
<li><strong>2-Room Apartment (B5) Sleeps 2-5:</strong> 1 twin bedroom and living/dining room with up to 3 convertible beds. Dishwasher. Some 2-room apartments also have Matterhorn view.</li>
</ul>]]></roomsDescription>
